ZH: 那家厂子每天排放大量的污水。
EN: That factory discharges a large amount of sewage every day.

ZH: 这个地区的污水处理设施需要升级。
EN: The sewage treatment facilities in this area need to be upgraded.

ZH: 污水流向了附近的河流。
EN: The sewage flowed into the nearby river.

ZH: 这座城市的污水处理能力已经超过了预期。
EN: The sewage treatment capacity of this city has exceeded expectations.

ZH: 环保部门正在制定污水排放的新政策。
EN: The environmental protection department is formulating new policies for sewage discharge.

ZH: 这个城市建立了很多废水处理厂来处理污水。
EN: This city has built many wastewater treatment plants to handle sewage.

ZH: 这家工厂没有合法的污水处理许可证。
EN: This factory doesn't have a valid sewage treatment permit.

ZH: 污水排放对附近的海洋生态系统造成了严重影响。
EN: Sewage discharge has had a serious impact on the nearby marine ecosystem.

ZH: 该地区的居民抗议工业区的污水污染问题。
EN: Residents in the area protested against the industrial zone's sewage pollution problem.

ZH: 我们需要采取措施减少污水的排放。
EN: We need to take measures to reduce sewage discharge.

ZH: 工业生产会产生大量的污水。
EN: Industrial production generates a large amount of wastewater.

ZH: 许多农村地区缺乏污水处理设施。
EN: Many rural areas lack sewage treatment facilities.

ZH: 污水排放需要遵守相关的环保法规。
EN: Sewage discharge needs to comply with relevant environmental regulations.

ZH: 这条河的污水含有大量有害物质。
EN: The sewage in this river contains a large amount of harmful substances.

ZH: 污水排放对饮用水源构成了威胁。
EN: Sewage discharge poses a threat to drinking water sources.

ZH: 环保志愿者每个月都会清理河道中的污水。
EN: Environmental volunteers clean up the sewage in the river every month.

ZH: 合理处理污水可以最大限度地减少环境损害。
EN: Properly treating sewage can minimize environmental damage.

ZH: 该市政府正在投资建设新的污水处理设施。
EN: The municipal government is investing in the construction of new sewage treatment plants.

ZH: 这次爆炸导致了大量的污水泄漏。
EN: The explosion caused a large amount of sewage leakage.

ZH: 我们需要共同努力，控制污水的排放。
EN: We need to work together to control the discharge of sewage.
